sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant StorageInit as KServe Storage<br/>Initializer
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/443 TCP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over StorageInit,S3: Pre-startup: Model Loading (HF Detector)
    StorageInit->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts
    StorageInit->>HF: Write to /mnt/models

    Note over Client,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in Text Detection (Regex/PII)
    Client->>Istio: Text generation request
    Istio->>Orchestrator: Forward (mTLS)
    Orchestrator->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8080, No Auth
    Note right of BuiltIn: Regex matching:<br/>email, SSN, CC,<br/>phone, IP patterns
    BuiltIn-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>[{detection, score, span}]
    Orchestrator-->>Istio: Filtered/annotated response
    Istio-->>Client: Response

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace Model Inference
    Client->>Istio: Text generation request
    Istio->>Orchestrator: Forward (mTLS)
    Orchestrator->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8000, KServe auth
    Note right of HF: PyTorch inference:<br/>AutoModel* classification<br/>or GraniteForCausalLM
    HF-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>[{detection, score, evidence}]
    Orchestrator-->>Istio: Filtered/annotated response
    Istio-->>Client: Response

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    Client->>Istio: Text generation request
    Istio->>Orchestrator: Forward (mTLS)
    Orchestrator->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/8000, KServe auth
    Judge->>vLLM: OpenAI-compatible API call<br/>HTTP/8080, No Auth
    vLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation result
    Judge-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse<br/>[{detection, score, evidence}]
    Orchestrator-->>Istio: Filtered/annotated response
    Istio-->>Client: Response
